        <ab>
          <lb n="1"/>
          <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>
        </ab>
        <p>
      			nanti-p-pōttarai
      			<lb break="no" n="2"/>carkku-p patiṉāṉk-āvatu
      		</p>
        <p>
      			I
      			<lb break="no" n="3"/>p-paḷḷi-Uṭai-Ārai nīkki Irun
      			<lb break="no" n="4"/>ta tavacikaḷukku-p piccai Eḻu
      			<lb n="5"/>kaḻañcu poṉ Ivv-ūr antai I
      			<lb break="no" n="6"/>ḷaiyār appaṇanti vaitta Aṟam
      		</p>
        <p>
      			<lb n="7"/>kaḻañciṉā<supplied reason="omitted">l</supplied> Uḻakk’ arici muṉ kuṟaṭṭi
      			<lb n="8"/>vaittatu
      		</p>
        <p>
      			Ivv-aṟam ūrōṅ kāp
      			<lb break="no" n="9"/>pōm āka Oṭṭiṉōṅ kāmakkō
      			<lb break="no" n="10"/>ṭṭam aḻitta pāvam āka Oṭṭiṟ 2 nā
      			<lb break="no" n="11"/>l-vāy uḻakk’ arici-Um muṭṭiṟ kō-Iṟku
      			<lb n="12"/>nāḷ-vāy oru kāṭi neṟṟaṇṭam
      		</p>
        <p>
      			<lb n="13"/>Ip-poṉ ṟaṭṭārkkulam paṭātu
      		</p>
